  "body": "<!-- If you need help or think you have found a bug, please help us with your issue by entering the following information (otherwise you can delete this text): -->\r\n\r\nOutput of `helm version`:\r\n```\r\n$ helm3 version\r\nversion.BuildInfo{Version:\"v3.0.0-beta.3\", GitCommit:\"5cb923eecbe80d1ad76399aee234717c11931d9a\", GitTreeState:\"clean\", GoVersion:\"go1.12.9\"}\r\n\r\n$ helm version --client\r\nClient: &version.Version{SemVer:\"v2.14.3\", GitCommit:\"0e7f3b6637f7af8fcfddb3d2941fcc7cbebb0085\", GitTreeState:\"clean\"}\r\n```\r\nOutput of `kubectl version`:\r\nN/A\r\n\r\nCloud Provider/Platform (AKS, GKE, Minikube etc.): \r\nN/A\r\n\r\n----\r\n\r\nIf you try to lint a packaged chart that doesn't exist, helm3 silently ignores it.\r\n \r\n```\r\n$ helm3 lint aaa-1.0.0.tgz\r\n==> Linting aaa-1.0.0.tgz\r\n\r\n1 chart(s) linted, 0 chart(s) failed\r\n```\r\n\r\n```\r\n$ helm lint aaa-1.0.0.tgz\r\n==> Skipping aaa-1.0.0.tgz\r\nopen aaa-1.0.0.tgz: no such file or directory\r\n\r\n0 chart(s) linted, no failures\r\n```",
